  --------------+----------------------------------------------------------
  FNOP		| Floating-Point No-Operation
  FREM		| IEEE Remainder
  FRESTORE	| Restore Floating-Point Internal State
  FSAVE		| Save Floating-Point Internal State
  FSCALE	| Floating-Point Scale Exponent
